title: Where to take your dog in Bratislava
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary: Travelling with your dog? Dave Rubin is a proud dog owner and knows all the best dog-friendly places in Bratislava. You should not be surprised if you see dogs in most shopping malls, restaurants, and cafes. If you want to give your dog a special treat, a dog cafe in Petrzalka might be the place for you and your furry companion.
